title: Chattahoochee River National Recreation Area: Frogs
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Animals     Amphibians     Frogs                  Frogs and Toads         Green Treefrog (Hyla cinerea) NPS Photo  The park is home to several species of frogs and toads- click below for field guides to some of them. Did you know all toads are frogs, but not all frogs are toads?
